{"tid":1524810,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[溫故知新]新加坡香口膠地鐵禁令","createTime":"2019-08-31T18:17:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T01:12:41.000Z","uid":30678,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c182d670487768e5edf785f6488cd6555da231e0","tid":1524810,"uid":30678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:17:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E5%8F%A3%E9%A6%99%E7%B3%96%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%259D%25A1%25E5%258F%25A3%25E9%25A6%2599%25E7%25B3%2596%25E7%25A6%2581%25E4%25BB%25A4&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70rPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=18390dd2\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E5%8F%A3%E9%A6%99%E7%B3%96%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A4</a><br />\n新加坡地鐵和禁令的實施<br />\n<br />\n1987年，耗資50億新元建造的新加坡地鐵投入使用。這在當時是新加坡實行的最大公共項目。後來據報導，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一些破壞者把吃剩的口香糖粘在地鐵車門的傳感器上，使車門無法正常運作，影響到地鐵服務。雖然此現象非常少見，但維護需要極高的費用</span></span>，也很難抓到破壞者。1992年，剛接任新加坡總理的吳作棟決定發布口香糖禁令。這一禁令隨《製造控制法》頒布，此法律同時限定某些菸酒產品的銷售。[3]"},{"pid":"d63f3666e28724108dde56b328050367b2165f55","tid":1524810,"uid":30678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:19:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b76480d92383810d4e74502c7515c7761faadf","tid":1524810,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:19:44.000Z","msg":"我知大家好撚嬲, 因為我地冇清算黨鐵先搞到今日咁, 但係要記得今日要去春袋報仇, 黨鐵黎緊一齊再清算！香港人加油 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lz7uo3t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLz7uo3t.jpg&h=4ed7d51c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70rPG